document.full_text: southwest airlines could cancel 300 flights on sunday as it continues to inspect 79 aircraft from its boeing 737 fleet, after one of its planes with a gaping hole in the fuselage made an emergency landing, a company spokeswoman said.
document.title: southwest may cancel another 300 flights sunday
